app_description: Meet people with InterPals the original culture and language exchange community with 5 million users. Chat with new friends pen pals and language partners from all over the world. Practice languages with native speakers to learn English Spanish French Japanese Korean Mandarin Chinese Cantonese Portuguese German Italian Russian Arabic Turkish and hundreds more all for FREE!
